attr.title: LISA: The Undone
attr.desc: LISA: The Undone is a fangame set in the LISA universe made by Redisco.
attr.desc_md: LISA: The Undone is a fangame set in the LISA universe made by Redisco.
attr.inst:
download the game from Gamejolt(https://gamejolt.com/games/dreamsofstars/696084) or itch(https://redisco.itch.io/lisa-the-undone) for free tested with Windows version. Copy all contents of the UNDONE folder from the download to the gamedata folder.

Note: This game is not ideal for devices with low resolution displays and/or absent joysticks.
attr.inst_md:
Download the game for free from [GameJolt](https://gamejolt.com/games/dreamsofstars/696084) or [itch.io](https://redisco.itch.io/lisa-the-undone) (tested with Windows version). Copy all contents of the UNDONE folder from the download to the gamedata folder.

**Note:** This game is not ideal for devices with low resolution displays and/or absent joysticks.
